{"id":330094,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/01/nbspnbsp/","date":"2014-01-17T07:48:00Z","modified":"2014-01-17T07:48:00Z","title":"&#20911;&#23398;&#33635; | &#20911;&#23398;&#33635;&amp;nbsp;*&#24494;&#35821;&#24405;*&amp;nbsp;&#65288;&#20108;&#65289;","content":"<p><p align=\"center\">\n<span>冯</span><span>学荣<br />\n*微</span><span>语录</span><span>*<br />\n（</span><span>二</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n你</span><span>认识</span><span>的人收入比你高、中大</span><span>奖</span><span>、</span><span>挣</span><span>大</span><span>钱</span><span>，你千万不要嫉妒甚至怨恨，你</span><span>应该</span><span>高</span><span>兴</span><span>，不是</span><span>为</span><span>他高</span><span>兴</span><span>，而是</span><span>为</span><span>你自己高</span><span>兴</span><span>，因</span><span>为</span><span>他有</span><span>钱</span><span>了，就不会找你借</span><span>钱</span><span>。同理，小区的搬运工、家政、粉刷匠</span><span>涨</span><span>价了，也不要生气，相反，你</span><span>应该</span><span>高</span><span>兴</span><span>，因</span><span>为</span><span>底</span><span>层</span><span>老百姓的收入越高，社会治安就越好，你和你家人的人身</span><span>财产</span><span>，就越安全。</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><span><br />\n“国民党</span><span>统</span><span>一中国有功”</span><span>，</span><span>这话对吗</span><span>？</span><span>正确的说法应该是：“国民党先造成的分裂、然后再营造统一”。北洋政府时期中国</span><span>分裂的局面</span><span>，</span><span>很大程度上就是</span><span>这</span><span>帮</span><span>国民</span><span>党人造成的。《</span><span>临时约</span><span>法》本身就有</span><span>问题</span><span>，它</span><span>过</span><span>分</span><span>强调约</span><span>束</span><span>总统</span><span>，但</span><span>对总统</span><span>和</span><span>总</span><span>理</span><span>权</span><span>限划分不清，</span><span>给</span><span>北洋</span><span>的</span><span>分裂埋下伏笔。其次，内</span><span>战</span><span>第一</span><span>枪</span><span>（二次革命）、</span><span>护</span><span>国、</span><span>护</span><span>法，两次粤桂</span><span>战</span><span>争…</span><span>..</span><span>&#8230;相当多的内</span><span>战</span><span>、分裂行</span><span>为</span><span>，</span><span>都是</span><span>国民</span><span>党一手打响的。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>海峡两岸</span><span>诟</span><span>病北洋</span><span>军阀</span><span>混</span><span>战</span><span>、民不聊生</span><span>。</span><span>可是</span><span>，</span><span>北洋</span><span>军阀为</span><span>什么混</span><span>战</span><span>？</span><span>其实</span><span>正是因</span><span>为</span><span>南方</span><span>国民党</span><span>势</span><span>力在</span><span>捣</span><span>乱。</span><span>其中，</span><span>直皖</span><span>战</span><span>争就是因</span><span>为</span><span>直系和皖系在</span><span>“</span><span>对孙</span><span>文是武力</span><span>镇压还</span><span>是和平</span><span>谈</span><span>判</span><span>”这个</span><span>问题</span><span>上</span><span>谈</span><span>不</span><span>拢</span><span>、</span><span>而开始交</span><span>恶</span><span>、并</span><span>逐</span><span>渐</span><span>走向</span><span>战</span><span>争</span><span>，在此过程中，南方阵营还给直系送了贿赂、进一步加剧了北洋集团的分裂</span><span>。而直奉</span><span>战</span><span>争</span><span>，那</span><span>就更赤裸了：</span><span>孙</span><span>文和段祺瑞、</span><span>张</span><span>作霖</span><span>结</span><span>成三角</span><span>联</span><span>盟</span><span>，共同</span><span>对</span><span>抗直系，</span><span>换</span><span>言之，</span><span>孙</span><span>文</span><span>本身</span><span>就是直奉</span><span>战</span><span>争</span><span>、内战分裂</span><span>的</span><span>一个积极</span><span>参与者。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n假</span><span>设</span><span>晚清立</span><span>宪</span><span>成功，那么</span><span>满</span><span>族皇帝</span><span>也许会</span><span>成</span><span>为</span><span>一个虚君，中国</span><span>也许</span><span>会</span><span>进</span><span>入代</span><span>议</span><span>政治，</span><span>汉</span><span>族人口占大多数，代</span><span>议</span><span>政治的可</span><span>预见结</span><span>果就是：国事由</span><span>汉</span><span>人</span><span>说</span><span>了算。不少</span><span>历</span><span>史</span><span>爱</span><span>好者没能看到</span><span>这</span><span>一点，逢</span><span>满</span><span>清必反，</span><span>这</span><span>是从意</span><span>识</span><span>形</span><span>态</span><span>出</span><span>发</span><span>看</span><span>问题</span><span>，而不是从老百姓的切身利益出</span><span>发</span><span>看</span><span>问题</span><span>，</span><span>为</span><span>反清而反清，而不是</span><span>为</span><span>利益去反清，事情就</span><span>变</span><span>味了。</span><span>当然，历史是不能假设的，此贴权当废话。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>张勋</span><span>复辟被</span><span>镇压</span><span>之后，段祺瑞拒</span><span>绝</span><span>恢复《</span><span>临时约</span><span>法》，段祺瑞的理由是</span><span>这样</span><span>的：辛亥革命所</span><span>缔</span><span>造的中</span><span>华</span><span>民国，在宣</span><span>统</span><span>复辟</span><span>时</span><span>，</span><span>就已</span><span>经灭</span><span>亡</span><span>了</span><span>，</span><span>而段祺瑞</span><span>讨</span><span>伐</span><span>张勋</span><span>成功，是“再造民国”，既然是</span><span>“</span><span>再造</span><span>”</span><span>，那么</span><span>，段祺瑞</span><span>自然有</span><span>权</span><span>重新制定</span><span>约</span><span>法，因此不必恢复</span><span>临时约</span><span>法</span><span>。这种说法，不能说一点道理都没有。再说了，临时约法本身也不是一部优秀的宪法性文件，甚至它的合法性，都值得商榷</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n江西</span><span>苏</span><span>区的</span><span>农</span><span>民当然是不愿意</span><span>红军</span><span>撤走的，首先</span><span>，</span><span>农</span><span>民打土豪之后，分到了土地，</span><span>这</span><span>些属于不</span><span>义</span><span>之</span><span>财</span><span>，</span><span>红军</span><span>一走，国民党地主武装回来，会将不</span><span>义</span><span>之</span><span>财</span><span>收回。其次，</span><span>许</span><span>多</span><span>农</span><span>民</span><span>为红军</span><span>服</span><span>务</span><span>，</span><span>实际</span><span>上已</span><span>经</span><span>在</span><span>颠</span><span>覆国家政</span><span>权</span><span>犯罪中</span><span>，</span><span>构成了共犯，国民党一回来，要被追究，甚至</span><span>枪毙</span><span>。《十送</span><span>红军</span><span>》之</span><span>类</span><span>的歌曲背后，</span><span>就</span><span>是</span><span>这样</span><span>的真相。</span><span>依依不舍的不是情感，而是利益。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n新加坡自古以来就是</span><span>马</span><span>来人的地</span><span>盘</span><span>，自明代以来福建移民如</span><span>过</span><span>江之</span><span>鲫</span><span>涌</span><span>进</span><span>来，</span><span>抢了</span><span>了</span><span>马</span><span>来人的</span><span>饭</span><span>碗。</span><span>马</span><span>来西</span><span>亚</span><span>立国之后，定下了</span><span>“</span><span>土著人</span><span>优</span><span>先</span><span>”</span><span>的国策，以李光耀</span><span>为</span><span>首的</span><span>华</span><span>人不服</span><span>从</span><span>中央号令，</span><span>马</span><span>来西</span><span>亚</span><span>决定壮士断臂、不要新加坡</span><span>这块领</span><span>土</span><span>了</span><span>、</span><span>让华</span><span>人自己玩去。</span><span>这样</span><span>，</span><span>才有</span><span>了</span><span>新加坡的</span><span>诞</span><span>生。如果</span><span>领</span><span>土主</span><span>权</span><span>不能商量，</span><span>则</span><span>不会有新加坡。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n“</span><span>领</span><span>土主</span><span>权</span><span>不可商量”的教条，只能在中国近代</span><span>“</span><span>受害史</span><span>观</span><span>”</span><span>的</span><span>语境里，</span><span>才能成立，在世界上并不</span><span>绝对</span><span>通行。如果</span><span>领</span><span>土主</span><span>权绝对</span><span>不可商量，</span><span>则</span><span>没有阿拉斯加的</span><span>领</span><span>土</span><span>买卖</span><span>，以色列的建国也无从</span><span>谈</span><span>起，欧盟</span><span>现在甚至</span><span>连</span><span>国界都拆了</span><span>，又如何解释？</span><span>荷</span><span>兰</span><span>、</span><span>马尔</span><span>代夫</span><span>这</span><span>些</span><span>领</span><span>土受海水威</span><span>胁</span><span>的国家，以后国土消失了，他</span><span>们</span><span>的人必然需要</span><span>购买</span><span>一</span><span>块</span><span>土地建国，</span><span>谁卖给</span><span>他？</span><span>他们届时怎么办？</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>钓鱼岛</span><span>，我一向主</span><span>张</span><span>：“依照</span><span>获</span><span>利最大方案</span><span>处</span><span>理”，</span><span>换</span><span>言之，是从中日两国邦交的全</span><span>盘</span><span>利益出</span><span>发</span><span>，</span><span>统</span><span>筹</span><span>计</span><span>划。</span><span>战</span><span>或者不</span><span>战</span><span>，都要</span><span>计</span><span>算成本和收益，看看哪个最有利。而从小受“</span><span>领</span><span>土主</span><span>权</span><span>不可商量”教育</span><span>长</span><span>大的保</span><span>钓</span><span>青年，</span><span>脑</span><span>袋已</span><span>经</span><span>僵化到“不惜一切保</span><span>卫钓鱼岛</span><span>”的地步、就算</span><span>丢</span><span>掉西瓜、也要</span><span>捡</span><span>芝麻，</span><span>“就算大陆不长草、也要收回钓鱼岛”</span><span>。</span><span>这种“爱国”病，已经到了放弃治疗的阶段了。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n“</span><span>领土</span><span>问题</span><span>绝对</span><span>不能商量”</span><span>，</span><span>这</span><span>种看似</span><span>十分</span><span>正确的</span><span>论调</span><span>，其</span><span>实</span><span>是</span><span>错</span><span>的，事</span><span>实</span><span>上中国也并没有做到：例如香港，在1949年放着不去“解放”</span><span>它</span><span>、偏偏要等到1997年才去收回</span><span>它</span><span>，</span><span>这</span><span>本身就是一种妥</span><span>协</span><span>和商量。21世</span><span>纪</span><span>初</span><span>，</span><span>中国与俄</span><span>罗</span><span>斯</span><span>签署</span><span>了</span><span>领</span><span>土划界</span><span>协</span><span>定</span><span>、放弃了一些有争议的土地</span><span>，</span><span>这</span><span>也是一种商量。所以</span><span>，</span><span>我</span><span>认为</span><span>正确的提法</span><span>应该</span><span>是：有争</span><span>议</span><span>的</span><span>领</span><span>土主</span><span>权</span><span>，可以商量解决。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n朋友批</span><span>评</span><span>得</span><span>对</span><span>，我的文字的确缺乏感情。但是搞</span><span>历史的，</span><span>不需要感情。只有</span><span>艺术创</span><span>作才需要感情。你</span><span>见过</span><span>修</span><span>车</span><span>技工</span><span>带</span><span>着感情去修</span><span>车吗</span><span>？</span><span>你见过医生一边泪流满面一边动手术的吗？</span><span>历</span><span>史上有</span><span>过带</span><span>感情写史的，</span><span>例如</span><span>梁启超的《戊戌政</span><span>变记</span><span>》就是，可是后来</span><span>，连梁启超</span><span>自己都</span><span>觉</span><span>得不妥、</span><span>他主动</span><span>反思</span><span>说</span><span>：当年</span><span>我</span><span>带</span><span>着</span><span>感情写《戊戌政</span><span>变记</span><span>》、</span><span>这本</span><span>书</span><span>失</span><span>实</span><span>，不能当</span><span>作</span><span>信史</span><span>来读</span><span>。</span><span>不料已经晚了，《戊戌政变记》这本伪史，已经广泛传播在民间、它里面的许多谎言，已经深入读者的骨髓了。历史证明了：</span><span>带</span><span>着</span><span>感情写史</span><span>，</span><span>不但不必，而且有害。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n那么多的科学家在研究延</span><span>缓</span><span>衰老的</span><span>办</span><span>法。阻</span><span>挡</span><span>衰老没有</span><span>错</span><span>。但人是不可能做到永生的。就算科学成功阻</span><span>挡</span><span>了衰老，人始</span><span>终还</span><span>是</span><span>难</span><span>免一死。道理其</span><span>实</span><span>很</span><span>简单</span><span>：人的死法除了病死之外，</span><span>还</span><span>有意外事故死亡、自</span><span>杀</span><span>他</span><span>杀</span><span>、食物中毒等一大堆死法。尤其是意外事故，它的概率是</span><span>客观</span><span>存在的，只要你我活得足</span><span>够长</span><span>，</span><span>迟</span><span>早也会</span><span>轮</span><span>到</span><span>你我的</span><span>头</span><span>上。</span><span>总之，无论科学如何发达，人终究是难免一死。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>传统</span><span>教育唆使孩子</span><span>们长</span><span>大之后“干大事”，</span><span>诸</span><span>如什么“</span><span>为</span><span>中</span><span>华</span><span>崛起</span><span>读书</span><span>”之</span><span>类</span><span>假大空的</span><span>东东</span><span>。将来</span><span>谁</span><span>教我小孩</span><span>长</span><span>大“干大事”，我就跟</span><span>谁</span><span>急。“干大事”的教育是有</span><span>问题</span><span>的。我</span><span>们应该</span><span>教育下一代“干小事”，而且要把小事干好。唱歌的好好唱。</span><span>杂</span><span>交水稻的</span><span>给</span><span>我好好交。</span><span>写史的给我好好写。打酱油的给我好好打。</span><span>精益求精，把无数的小事干精了，自然</span><span>也就</span><span>成就</span><span>了</span><span>大事。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n不要</span><span>总</span><span>拿</span><span>辫</span><span>子</span><span>说</span><span>事，</span><span>辫</span><span>子在近代受国内外人士歧</span><span>视</span><span>，主要不是因</span><span>为辫</span><span>子丑陋，而是因</span><span>为</span><span>大清国落后、被人看不起，</span><span>所以</span><span>辫</span><span>子</span><span>才</span><span>成</span><span>为</span><span>众矢之的。</span><span>换个说法：假设当年的大清国硬实力、软实力都世界第一的话，那么辫子不但不被人笑话，而且还会成为时尚。试问</span><span>各位是否留意：你我</span><span>现</span><span>在留的短</span><span>发</span><span>，也是异族</span><span>的</span><span>发</span><span>型，它</span><span>并</span><span>不是中国人</span><span>的</span><span>传统发</span><span>型</span><span>、更不是汉人的传统发型</span><span>。</span><span>我们汉人的传统发型是长发，男的留长发。</span><span>中国</span><span>历</span><span>朝</span><span>历</span><span>代，</span><span>都</span><span>没有短</span><span>发</span><span>的，短</span><span>发</span><span>是</span><span>模仿</span><span>西方人的</span><span>发</span><span>型。</span><span>为</span><span>何留短</span><span>发</span><span>不羞耻？因</span><span>为</span><span>西方代表了先</span><span>进</span><span>。</span><span>那些号称爱国的极端民族主义分子，你先把你的长发给我留起来再说话。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>清末民初</span><span>时</span><span>代中国的一</span><span>块钱</span><span>大</span><span>约兑换</span><span>日元一</span><span>块</span><span>一毛</span><span>钱</span><span>，日本的物价比中国低，</span><span>这</span><span>是众多</span><span>归</span><span>国留日学生回</span><span>忆录</span><span>所</span><span>共同指</span><span>证</span><span>的事</span><span>实</span><span>。当</span><span>时</span><span>中国的</span><span>劳动</span><span>力价格并不低，</span><span>旧中国</span><span>一个黄包</span><span>车</span><span>夫一个月的收入，可以养活一家老小好几口人，</span><span>现</span><span>在</span><span>呢？</span><span>内地摩托</span><span>车载</span><span>客</span><span>，</span><span>一个月只能</span><span>挣</span><span>两千元左右，</span><span>东</span><span>莞工厂工人月入也是</span><span>顶多三</span><span>千</span><span>元</span><span>，</span><span>连</span><span>养</span><span>活</span><span>自己都成</span><span>问题</span><span>。</span><span>到底谁是“水深火热”？</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>我因</span><span>为</span><span>写了不少揭</span><span>孙</span><span>中山短</span><span>处</span><span>的文字，不断掉粉，但是我</span><span>认为</span><span>我没有</span><span>错</span><span>。我</span><span>批判</span><span>孙</span><span>文，并非</span><span>因为</span><span>我和他有仇，而是</span><span>这</span><span>个人打着</span><span>爱</span><span>国的口号，折</span><span>腾</span><span>了</span><span>这</span><span>个国家几十年，不但没能</span><span>给</span><span>广大老百姓</span><span>带</span><span>来什么</span><span>实</span><span>惠，而且</span><span>还</span><span>造成遍地流血、也阻碍了工商生</span><span>产</span><span>。政治是</span><span>讲</span><span>利益的，没有</span><span>给</span><span>老百姓</span><span>带</span><span>来</span><span>实</span><span>惠的政治家，</span><span>就不是一个好的政治家，也就</span><span>没有理由</span><span>值</span><span>得人</span><span>们怀</span><span>念。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n第一等的事是</span><span>“</span><span>利人利己</span><span>”</span><span>，例如生</span><span>产</span><span>和交</span><span>换</span><span>，要鼓励多做。第二等的事是</span><span>“</span><span>损</span><span>已利人</span><span>”</span><span>，例如扶弱救</span><span>贫</span><span>，也要适当做一点，但只能列</span><span>为</span><span>二等事</span><span>业</span><span>，因</span><span>为</span><span>自力更生必</span><span>须</span><span>占主流，不能都依靠</span><span>别</span><span>人，</span><span>如果</span><span>人人</span><span>都</span><span>靠施舍，</span><span>那么</span><span>谁</span><span>来当施主？最下等的事情是</span><span>“</span><span>损</span><span>人不利己</span><span>”</span><span>的蠢事，例如上网和不相</span><span>识</span><span>的人</span><span>对骂</span><span>，就是</span><span>这类</span><span>“有成本、无收益”的</span><span>蠢事，</span><span>这类</span><span>蠢事</span><span>，绝对</span><span>不能做。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n脱</span><span>贫</span><span>最快的</span><span>办</span><span>法</span><span>，</span><span>是嫁</span><span>给</span><span>富人。同理，解决中国</span><span>问题</span><span>最快的</span><span>办</span><span>法是和美国合并，当然合并之后的国家不能叫“美国”，</span><span>应该</span><span>叫&#8221;Chimerica&#8221;、“中美合众国”，</span><span>这样</span><span>叫，双方都不吃</span><span>亏</span><span>。然后照搬美国政治体制，13</span><span>亿</span><span>人参与</span><span>选举</span><span>“中美合众国”</span><span>总统</span><span>。此方案兼</span><span>顾</span><span>了主</span><span>权</span><span>、民族感情、民主、法治，所有</span><span>问题</span><span>一夜之</span><span>间</span><span>全部解决</span><span>。当然，这活儿也许不好弄，但是至少在理论上，可以成立。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n所</span><span>谓</span><span>“</span><span>二十一条</span><span>”，</span><span>和山</span><span>东</span><span>有关的，正式名称叫《关于山</span><span>东</span><span>之条</span><span>约</span><span>》</span><span>，</span><span>中方</span><span>的</span><span>签</span><span>署人是</span><span>陆</span><span>征祥。那么</span><span>“</span><span>五四运</span><span>动</span><span>”的</span><span>学生</span><span>为</span><span>什么不</span><span>殴打</span><span>陆</span><span>征祥、而去</span><span>殴打</span><span>曹汝霖？因</span><span>为</span><span>爱国</span><span>学生</span><span>们</span><span>不知道那个条</span><span>约</span><span>是</span><span>陆</span><span>征祥</span><span>签</span><span>的，他</span><span>们</span><span>误</span><span>以</span><span>为</span><span>是曹汝霖</span><span>签</span><span>的，曹汝霖因</span><span>为</span><span>在外有</span><span>“</span><span>亲</span><span>日</span><span>”</span><span>的</span><span>坏</span><span>名声，所以</span><span>他</span><span>被学生冤枉。</span><span>可见，五四</span><span>学生</span><span>在</span><span>打人之前，</span><span>连</span><span>施暴</span><span>对</span><span>象都没有弄清楚，人</span><span>间</span><span>笑</span><span>话</span><span>，</span><span>莫</span><span>过</span><span>于此。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n那些</span><span>认为</span><span>“宁愿坐在宝</span><span>马车</span><span>里哭，也不愿坐在自行</span><span>车</span><span>后笑”的美女，是否懂得一个</span><span>简单</span><span>的</span><span>经济</span><span>学道理：你的美色一年比一年衰老。而你的富豪老公</span><span>财</span><span>富是一年比一年多。</span><span>换</span><span>言之，他是潜力股，而你是</span><span>负资产</span><span>。</span><span>你看中他的钱，他会不知道？别傻了。</span><span>长</span><span>期以往，他</span><span>总</span><span>有醒悟的</span><span>时</span><span>候、</span><span>他</span><span>必然</span><span>会</span><span>心理失衡，</span><span>也</span><span>必然</span><span>会</span><span>外出</span><span>偷</span><span>腥。</span><span>等到有一天，你发现你会和一群妓女分享一个男人的时候，你就知道“惨”字怎么写了。当然，你永远不会知道，因为他偷腥不会告诉你。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n上千元一件的名牌服装，是几十元成本的</span><span>东</span><span>莞制造。</span><span>鲍</span><span>参</span><span>鱼</span><span>翅，</span><span>已经被科学证明：</span><span>营</span><span>养</span><span>反而</span><span>不如最便宜的豆腐、白菜、</span><span>鸡</span><span>蛋。再大再漂亮的新房子，住一两个月就</span><span>会</span><span>厌</span><span>倦，小房子住</span><span>惯</span><span>了反而很舒服；至于外出，恕我直言，开小</span><span>车</span><span>、</span><span>坐</span><span>飞</span><span>机越多，死亡</span><span>的</span><span>机会</span><span>就</span><span>越大。女色</span><span>那</span><span>就更不用</span><span>说</span><span>了，25</span><span>岁</span><span>以后，色相开始</span><span>迅速</span><span>变质</span><span>。人</span><span>，</span><span>要从物</span><span>质</span><span>世界</span><span>里面去</span><span>寻</span><span>找幸福，</span><span>其实</span><span>并不明智。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>孙</span><span>文一生干暴力革命，到底是</span><span>为</span><span>国</span><span>为</span><span>民，</span><span>还</span><span>是</span><span>为</span><span>了他自己掌</span><span>权</span><span>？在</span><span>这</span><span>个</span><span>问题</span><span>上</span><span>，我认为</span><span>不宜走极端。从第一手史料</span><span>记录</span><span>的</span><span>孙</span><span>文一生言行来看，我</span><span>认为</span><span>比</span><span>较</span><span>靠</span><span>谱</span><span>的看法是：二者兼有之。二者也并不矛盾。那么</span><span>，</span><span>到底</span><span>他</span><span>是</span><span>爱</span><span>国成分多一点、</span><span>还</span><span>是</span><span>权</span><span>欲</span><span>成分</span><span>多一点？</span><span>这</span><span>个</span><span>问题</span><span>涉及到他的主</span><span>观</span><span>意</span><span>识</span><span>，</span><span>我想</span><span>恐怕是无法</span><span>证</span><span>明的，</span><span>也许</span><span>甚至</span><span>连</span><span>他自己</span><span>，</span><span>也未必有</span><span>清晰的</span><span>答案</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>不少</span><span>历</span><span>史</span><span>爱</span><span>好者乃至研究者</span><span>，</span><span>无限推崇《</span><span>临时约</span><span>法》、将</span><span>这</span><span>部</span><span>约</span><span>法的效力神化、道德化、宗教化了。其</span><span>实这</span><span>部</span><span>约</span><span>法的效力有待商榷。通</span><span>过这</span><span>部</span><span>约</span><span>法的，是在辛亥</span><span>战</span><span>火中</span><span>组</span><span>建的</span><span>“</span><span>临时</span><span>参</span><span>议</span><span>院</span><span>”</span><span>，</span><span>“议员”是</span><span>来自五湖四海的四十多名代表，并非是民</span><span>选</span><span>的，而是赶来南京参加革命的，所以他</span><span>们</span><span>叫</span><span>做</span><span>“</span><span>临时</span><span>参</span><span>议</span><span>院”，制定的</span><span>约</span><span>法</span><span>也只能</span><span>叫</span><span>做</span><span>《</span><span>临时约</span><span>法》。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n用</span><span>钱</span><span>解决</span><span>问题</span><span>，</span><span>当然不</span><span>够</span><span>好，但</span><span>是</span><span>总</span><span>比用暴力解决</span><span>问题强</span><span>。当年</span><span>，</span><span>段祺瑞</span><span>给</span><span>安福</span><span>议员发钱</span><span>、曹</span><span>锟贿赂议员选</span><span>自己当</span><span>总统</span><span>，乍一看</span><span>，</span><span>相当</span><span>的</span><span>荒唐，但</span><span>是，</span><span>这</span><span>恰恰是</span><span>进</span><span>步，因</span><span>为</span><span>暴力开始逐</span><span>渐</span><span>不被使用，</span><span>对</span><span>于</span><span>这</span><span>种</span><span>选举</span><span>违规</span><span>行</span><span>为</span><span>，</span><span>应该</span><span>用</span><span>舆论</span><span>、法律、散步等各种</span><span>和平</span><span>手段去抵制它、逼迫它改良，但是</span><span>，</span><span>有人采取了暴力手段，</span><span>结</span><span>果</span><span>造成了</span><span>暴徒上台</span><span>，反而</span><span>一代不如一代。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n不少人把网</span><span>络</span><span>看作</span><span>战场</span><span>，一上来就判定是非、到</span><span>处骂</span><span>人</span><span>树敌</span><span>&#8230;</span><span>..</span><span>..</span><span>这</span><span>就是意</span><span>识</span><span>形</span><span>态</span><span>教育下的残渣。事</span><span>实</span><span>上，网</span><span>络应该</span><span>是一个自由开放的</span><span>跳蚤</span><span>市</span><span>场</span><span>、是一个交</span><span>换</span><span>所需的平台。交</span><span>换</span><span>什么？交</span><span>换</span><span>的是信息。一个个博主，</span><span>就</span><span>是一个个的小</span><span>贩</span><span>，挑肥</span><span>拣</span><span>瘦，各取所需，在交</span><span>换</span><span>的</span><span>过</span><span>程中，所有人的信息量都增大了，</span><span>这</span><span>才是网</span><span>络</span><span>的真正意</span><span>义</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n有人</span><span>说</span><span>自由无价，但若有人出一万元</span><span>让</span><span>你</span><span>坐牢一天，相信不少人愿意干。有人</span><span>说</span><span>友情无价，但当有人出一</span><span>亿</span><span>元</span><span>让远</span><span>离一</span><span>个</span><span>朋友，也有人肯干。就算生命也是有价的，否</span><span>则</span><span>拆</span><span>弹员</span><span>、挖煤</span><span>矿</span><span>一类的工作就</span><span>不会高薪。我的</span><span>话</span><span>不好听，但却是</span><span>大</span><span>实话</span><span>。一个万物有价的</span><span>资</span><span>本主</span><span>义</span><span>社会，</span><span>虽</span><span>然冷漠无情，但</span><span>它</span><span>却是一个和平的社会，因</span><span>为钱</span><span>能解决一切</span><span>问题</span><span>。</span><span>钱能解决问题了，问题反而更少了。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>人</span><span>类</span><span>之所以</span><span>纷</span><span>争不断，在于</span><span>认为</span><span>有些</span><span>东</span><span>西是</span><span>“</span><span>无价</span><span>”</span><span>的、</span><span>是通过</span><span>谈</span><span>判无法解决</span><span>的</span><span>、</span><span>而</span><span>必</span><span>须诉诸</span><span>武力</span><span>的。</span><span>这</span><span>些所</span><span>谓</span><span>“</span><span>无价</span><span>”</span><span>的</span><span>东</span><span>西，例如</span><span>领</span><span>土、</span><span>贞</span><span>操、面子等</span><span>。但是事实上，</span><span>贞</span><span>操</span><span>是</span><span>有价</span><span>的</span><span>，美女多嫁富豪</span><span>，</span><span>即</span><span>为</span><span>明</span><span>证</span><span>。领土也是有价的，人类历史上领土买卖的案件，不止一起。</span><span>人</span><span>类应该</span><span>在自由</span><span>贸</span><span>易中逐</span><span>渐</span><span>懂得：世上一切都是有价的，因此都是可以商量的，没有</span><span>谈</span><span>不</span><span>拢</span><span>的事，如果用交</span><span>换</span><span>可以解决一切</span><span>问题</span><span>，人</span><span>类</span><span>社会</span><span>的纷争，自然就少</span><span>了。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n全球化的好</span><span>处</span><span>之一</span><span>，</span><span>是把各国的利益</span><span>搅</span><span>在了一起：你中有我，我中有你。</span><span>这样</span><span>的</span><span>经济</span><span>基</span><span>础</span><span>，</span><span>决定了狭隘民族主</span><span>义</span><span>的生存空</span><span>间</span><span>必然</span><span>会逐年</span><span>变</span><span>小，因</span><span>为</span><span>原本</span><span>“</span><span>各自</span><span>为</span><span>政</span><span>”</span><span>的利益</span><span>，</span><span>现</span><span>在</span><span>变</span><span>成</span><span>“</span><span>合伙</span><span>”</span><span>了，</span><span>标</span><span>准不同了。正因</span><span>为</span><span>如此，一切意</span><span>识</span><span>形</span><span>态</span><span>的</span><span>东</span><span>西</span><span>，</span><span>都</span><span>显得有点</span><span>不合</span><span>时</span><span>宜</span><span>了。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n近代史</span><span>说</span><span>：清末民初外</span><span>资</span><span>涌</span><span>进</span><span>中国，使小</span><span>农经济</span><span>破</span><span>产</span><span>（例如土布、蜡</span><span>烛</span><span>、挑夫）、</span><span>产</span><span>生了大量底</span><span>层</span><span>失</span><span>业</span><span>人</span><span>员</span><span>，事</span><span>实</span><span>是否如此？的确如此。但是，近代史没有</span><span>告诉你的是</span><span>：同</span><span>时</span><span>，外国</span><span>资</span><span>本在中国开</span><span>办</span><span>了大量</span><span>的</span><span>工厂、</span><span>创</span><span>造了大量的就</span><span>业</span><span>。1978年之后，同</span><span>样的事情，</span><span>在中国重演，</span><span>这</span><span>次却</span><span>变</span><span>成是合法的。事</span><span>实</span><span>基本不</span><span>变</span><span>，</span><span>是</span><span>立</span><span>场变</span><span>了。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n有人</span><span>说</span><span>：如果不推翻北洋政府、</span><span>让</span><span>它胡</span><span>闹</span><span>，</span><span>东</span><span>三省早就保不住了。</span><span>这</span><span>只是一个无法</span><span>证</span><span>明的假</span><span>设</span><span>。但是</span><span>铁的事实却是：</span><span>推翻了北洋政府、推行革命外交，就开始打外</span><span>战</span><span>，</span><span>东</span><span>三省（126万平方公里）</span><span>到底</span><span>是保住了，但是却失去了外蒙（156万平方公里）和中俄</span><span>边</span><span>界大片</span><span>的</span><span>争</span><span>议</span><span>地。收回了台湾，但是</span><span>也伤亡</span><span>了三千</span><span>多</span><span>万人。是否</span><span>值</span><span>得，有待商榷，</span><span>见</span><span>仁</span><span>见</span><span>智。</span><span>当然，有人认为中国的人命不值钱，那就没什么好说的了。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n北洋</span><span>时</span><span>代不喊“打倒帝国主</span><span>义</span><span>”。袁世</span><span>凯</span><span>、段祺瑞、</span><span>张</span><span>作霖表面上和帝国主</span><span>义</span><span>合作（</span><span>卖</span><span>国），</span><span>实际</span><span>上是</span><span>在</span><span>利用帝国主</span><span>义</span><span>、</span><span>为</span><span>自己服</span><span>务</span><span>。</span><span>苏</span><span>俄</span><span>势</span><span>力渗透中国之后，“打倒帝国主</span><span>义</span><span>”的口号才突然喊得空前响亮，外行人解</span><span>读为</span><span>国共两党“</span><span>爱</span><span>国”，</span><span>实际</span><span>上</span><span>这</span><span>个口号在当</span><span>时</span><span>，</span><span>是两党煽</span><span>动</span><span>人民</span><span>颠</span><span>覆“帝国主</span><span>义</span><span>走狗”北洋政府的工具。</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><span><br />\n在当今的大</span><span>陆</span><span>，去一个主</span><span>题</span><span>游</span><span>乐</span><span>公园玩一天，</span><span>门</span><span>票100－200元。</span><span>约</span><span>上猪朋狗友吃喝一</span><span>顿</span><span>，花</span><span>费</span><span>是500元。到上海夜</span><span>总</span><span>会</span><span>搂</span><span>个小姐唱个歌，坐台</span><span>费</span><span>据</span><span>说</span><span>是400元。</span><span>买</span><span>一个</span><span>东</span><span>莞生</span><span>产</span><span>的COACH手袋，</span><span>约</span><span>人民2000元。但是，</span><span>买</span><span>一本好</span><span>书</span><span>，只需要人民</span><span>币</span><span>38元，可以</span><span>读</span><span>两天，平均日消</span><span>费仅</span><span>需19元，既得到了精神享受、也增</span><span>长</span><span>了</span><span>见识</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n女人的</span><span>贞</span><span>操不能侵犯，但是它可以商量。当一个女人</span><span>爱</span><span>上你，那么她的</span><span>贞</span><span>操</span><span>对</span><span>于你来</span><span>说</span><span>，就是可以商量的，她的身体</span><span>对</span><span>你</span><span>，也</span><span>不再是禁区。同理，</span><span>领</span><span>土不能侵犯，但是可以商量，</span><span>这</span><span>个</span><span>观</span><span>念</span><span>应该</span><span>普及到全</span><span>人类</span><span>。</span><span>不少的人</span><span>把</span><span>领</span><span>土主</span><span>权</span><span>教条化、</span><span>宗教化</span><span>了，</span><span>这</span><span>是一个枷</span><span>锁</span><span>，也是</span><span>人类</span><span>战祸</span><span>不断的根源之一。土地在国家之</span><span>间</span><span>，</span><span>应该</span><span>是可以流</span><span>转</span><span>的。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>“崽</span><span>卖爷</span><span>田</span><span>”</span><span>在旧社会属于“</span><span>败</span><span>家”行</span><span>为</span><span>，受父老</span><span>乡亲</span><span>的</span><span>耻笑，但是</span><span>，</span><span>现</span><span>在社会</span><span>观</span><span>念</span><span>进</span><span>步了，</span><span>卖</span><span>掉祖屋用来投</span><span>资</span><span>做生意、或用来</span><span>购</span><span>置更好的房子，社会已</span><span>经</span><span>没有异</span><span>议</span><span>了</span><span>。</span><span>领</span><span>土也是同理，在市</span><span>场经济</span><span>的</span><span>逻辑</span><span>下，</span><span>领</span><span>土并不是不能</span><span>买卖</span><span>的。假如美国出一万</span><span>亿</span><span>美元</span><span>、</span><span>购买</span><span>我</span><span>们</span><span>100平方</span><span>米的</span><span>领</span><span>土，</span><span>卖不卖？</span><span>我</span><span>认为</span><span>是划算的</span><span>、当然可以卖</span><span>，关</span><span>键</span><span>是</span><span>：</span><span>卖</span><span>的</span><span>钱</span><span>，</span><span>要</span><span>分给</span><span>13</span><span>亿</span><span>人，</span><span>人人有份。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>对</span><span>于一个理</span><span>论</span><span>，</span><span>仅</span><span>凭他人的</span><span>说</span><span>教，不加以分析、不去</span><span>验证</span><span>，盲目取信，叫做“迷信”。同理，</span><span>对</span><span>于一个理</span><span>论</span><span>，不</span><span>让</span><span>人把</span><span>话说</span><span>完、打断</span><span>别</span><span>人的</span><span>话</span><span>、不加以分析、更不去</span><span>验证</span><span>，</span><span>仅</span><span>凭自己的喜好</span><span>、</span><span>固</span><span>执</span><span>地予以否定，</span><span>则</span><span>叫做“迷不信”。“迷不信”和“迷信”一</span><span>样</span><span>，</span><span>都</span><span>是愚昧的表</span><span>现</span><span>，它</span><span>们</span><span>都不是一个理性</span><span>人士</span><span>对</span><span>待事物</span><span>所应持有</span><span>的正确</span><span>态</span><span>度。</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><span><br />\n“</span><span>护</span><span>法”（保</span><span>护</span><span>《</span><span>临时约</span><span>法》）是否具</span><span>备绝对</span><span>的正当性？</span><span>我看</span><span>未必。</span><span>许</span><span>多国家都有修改</span><span>宪</span><span>法的行</span><span>为</span><span>。</span><span>试</span><span>想</span><span>：假设</span><span>中国在1984年修改</span><span>宪</span><span>法的</span><span>时</span><span>候，广</span><span>东</span><span>突然</span><span>冒出来一支</span><span>“</span><span>革命</span><span>军</span><span>”</span><span>，打出“</span><span>护</span><span>法”</span><span>的</span><span>大旗打内</span><span>战</span><span>，</span><span>这</span><span>有道理么？没有道理。况且《</span><span>临时约</span><span>法》并非一部</span><span>优</span><span>秀的</span><span>宪</span><span>法性文件，至少事后的《曹</span><span>锟宪</span><span>法》</span><span>，</span><span>就比《</span><span>临时约</span><span>法》更科学、更民主。</span><span>历史的本色是客观的，只是读史人戴上了不同颜色的眼镜去看它，所以历史的本色就变了。其实这并不困难，只要读史人愿意<u>摘下有色眼镜</u>，他就能读到一部真实的历史。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>冯学